" Enable or disable Syntastic Check
" Using :SyntasticToggleMode you can toggle Syntastic into passive mode, which
" will disable auto-checking. You can then check a file by running
" :SyntasticCheck instead.

silent! nmap <F7> :SyntasticToggleMode<CR>


